---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ContentPage from '../components/ContentPage.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Aevum Pets"
  description="Learn how Aevum Pets collects, uses, and protects your personal information."
>
  <ContentPage title="Privacy Policy" updated="February 1, 2026">
    <p class="text-xl" style="color: var(--color-slate-grey);">
      Your Privacy, Our Priority
    </p>
    <p>
      At Aevum Pets ("we," "us," "our"), we are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy
      explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you visit our website, www.aevumpets.com.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 my-4 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Information You Provide:</strong> This includes your name and email address when you sign up for our newsletter, submit a contact form, or participate in a survey.</li>
      <li><strong>Automatically Collected Information:</strong> We use cookies and similar technologies to collect non-personal data about your device and browsing behavior on our site (e.g., IP address, browser type, pages viewed). This helps us improve site functionality and user experience.</li>
      <li><strong>Third-Party Data:</strong> We may receive data from partners like social media platforms if you interact with our content there.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 my-4 space-y-2">
      <li>Provide, operate, and improve our website and content.</li>
      <li>Send you our curated newsletter (you can opt-out anytime).</li>
      <li>Respond to your inquiries and requests.</li>
      <li>Analyze site performance and trends to enhance your experience.</li>
      <li>Ensure the security of our website.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">3. How We Share Your Information</h2>
    <p>
      We <strong>do not sell</strong> your personal information. We may share it only in the following limited circumstances:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 my-4 space-y-2">
      <li>With trusted third-party service providers (e.g., email marketing platform, web hosting) who assist us under strict confidentiality agreements.</li>
      <li>If required by law or to protect our rights.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">4. Your Choices &amp; Rights</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 my-4 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Newsletter:</strong> You can unsubscribe using the link at the bottom of every email.</li>
      <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Most browsers allow you to control cookies through their settings.</li>
      <li><strong>Access/Deletion:</strong> You may request access to or deletion of your personal data by contacting us at <a href="mailto:privacy@aevumpets.com" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">privacy@aevumpets.com</a>.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">5. Data Security</h2>
    <p>
      We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information. However, no online transmission is 100% secure.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this policy periodically. The "Last Updated" date will reflect changes.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">7. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      For any privacy-related questions, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:privacy@aevumpets.com" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">privacy@aevumpets.com</a>.
    </p>
  </ContentPage>
</BaseLayout>
